settings.description: You find yourself in an unknown dimension, and you must find your ship. Will you escape, or will you stay here forever?

Fly, slide and spin through the sky and Bowser's castle!
(For Smaghetti Build Contest #2.)
Wendy gets her Airship redesigned, With various Airships added for assistant, Mario goes to the airship by using an mini airship instead of climbing, Good Luck Defeating Wendy & Finding a Secret Exit
Embarking a Journey on the First Unused level but It's Improved by a little bit, Good luck finding the hidden Ace coins!
Dodge the bullets, Touch the snake Corners, and defeat Lemmy, He has more lives and resistance to fire than ever before. Good luck defeating Lemmy and finding the secret exit!
A Klasky and fun Mario Adventure
While in his usual trips, Mario encounters a Bullet Bill field, filled to the brim with Bullet and Missile Bills. What powers and quirks will Mario find in his adventure?

Or does it blow east? Who knows. 

Prod. Code: 101, Rel: 5/19/22 - 8.35 PM
Mario tiene que conseguir el cofre antes que sea demasiado tarde
get to boom boom's hideout somewhere in the bunker and defeat him! (has bullet hell stuff, if you can even call it one)

A flood has happened in Pipe Maze! There is no explanation but you must get through the maze. It's easy to escape.
